reqBody.prompt: A cybernetic soldier, a protector of the digital realm. She wears a sleek, high-tech combat suit with glowing augmentations and dress boots. She has stylized, minimalist, anime-inspired eyes that are large and expressive with simplified details, focusing on conveying emotion through shape and limited shading. She is standing with her arms outstretched to the sides, palms facing downwards, and her legs slightly apart with a slight bend in her knees. Reference sheet. Deep black background.
